{"tid":2478182,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"連登CCTOY笑話紀錄大全（1）","createTime":"2021-04-07T00:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T01:01:14.000Z","uid":391580,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a163fcc1fc935909e68011be791575272d94c5c4","tid":2478182,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T00:24:21.000Z","msg":"從今日開始紀錄兒登仔嘅笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCCTOY兒登仔特徵<br />\n&bull; 無知<br />\n&bull; 鍾意攞未經證實嘅嘢打飛機<br />\n&bull; 屈毛<br />\n&bull; 覺得支那一無是處（但係又肯承認支那偷技術一流，即係自相矛盾，既然偷技術一流又點會冇技術呢？）<br />\n<br />\n兒登仔編號#227628 扮工署專員<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdEk4MczMzvPy8Ep1UZ8kuhoFCWrfSzJhKjBgRnNpeVz3?filename=MmGZTUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMmGZTUE.jpg&h=dd8fbc0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n名言：<br />\n中國因為冇美國芯片所以發射火箭失敗<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcbTQFA9fne5Pavt5KTDuBm5YbCL9fFaQS9cVzuUdghvQ?filename=m7mbK1M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7mbK1M.jpg&h=475e1d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP4ijQ4MJ8LRd3B1QM2my61f9JEvpWE2ZxF7uo1vxiZxz?filename=863hFz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F863hFz9.jpg&h=8fa639db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">明明係講緊年內三次佢就睇做連續三次</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實：原來2021年支國已經成功發射左七支火箭<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaRmQTSMbEkGdANXCFgBW8RFnzG61UATe2CLaxFEr3keq?filename=0PuTYno.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0PuTYno.jpg&h=5b07dafc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020年支國發射39支火箭，失敗3支<br />\n而2019年支國發射34支火箭，失敗2支<br />\n<br />\n結論，晶片限制根本冇影響，火箭根本唔需要用高密度晶片，有媒體斷章取義，捕風捉影<br />\n<br />\n例如用失敗三次好罕見（其實只不過係比2019年多一次，而且發射次數仲要多五支）<br />\n用網上人哋嘅輿論當作新聞（有人認為是不是美國晶片限制導致）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">結果兒登仔就全盤相信，係一啲學術討論post下面笑認為中共真係有一定水平火箭/太空科技嘅人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">請兒登仔認清楚支國水平，深入了解對手，唔好做井底之蛙，否則只會被人嘲笑，輕視對手亦都會付出重大嘅代價（雖然兒登仔冇咩代價可以付出）</span></span>"},{"pid":"547955c72ed81132f7bcd064ddeea290d13cc4f3","tid":2478182,"uid":391580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T00:28:42.000Z","msg":"兒登仔其中一個特徵<br />\n只要你講支那有技術<br />\n<br />\n佢就會話<br />\n<br />\n咁打台灣未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a473519b759b8f88cc803302a86d3da6533da57c","tid":2478182,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T00:34:09.000Z","msg":"又話自己唔 care 講到傷唔到你一條毛嘅<br />\n<br />\n就係睇死你會繼續開 post 發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0cc919423f8b82eeb6ae55ad4dcb9b6e1ce2e6","tid":2478182,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T00:34:43.000Z","msg":"鍾共打手勿回<br />\n<br />\n連登培生培心會員討論區（1）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2476780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2476780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n樓豬簡介：<br />\n- 用小米機<br />\n- 用支那 APP<br />\n- 用 HK01 賣港 APP<br />\n- 鍾共培生會粉絲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用小米機(仲要唔係一千以下)反共講出嚟知唔知醜<br />\n畀埋錢支企賺撐共就有你份<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmemgqePMhWydUc2rxg7daoYiPvjaeRZpA8TfMhXCexT3Z?filename=RSsFtA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSsFtA2.png&h=c68c0e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7e4bc122949792d2e91985af7b956cc728ccb12","tid":2478182,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T00:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/following/391580/20210402-2471976-3-實名反共-費事啲人話我用小米係五毛.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2Ffollowing%2F391580%2F20210402-2471976-3-%E5%AF%A6%E5%90%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%B1-%E8%B2%BB%E4%BA%8B%E5%95%B2%E4%BA%BA%E8%A9%B1%E6%88%91%E7%94%A8%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E4%BF%82%E4%BA%94%E6%AF%9B.png&h=e8070c7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n揸住部小米機話反共，人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n仲要係<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">小米10</span></strong></span>，大把外國牌子平機唔揀<br />\n揀部幾千蚊嘅小米機畀錢中共賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小米心諗最好全部反共嘅都買佢部機佢就 fat fat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有 $$$ 又有 data 送中一網打盡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會員編號：#391580<br />\n會員註冊日期：2021/2/3<br />\n入 LIST 原因：屢次自爆用小米機，用過嚟 check 自己嘢，仲有一堆支那 APP 不能盡錄，仲要係鍾共粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Flihkg_on9_list&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=3fe44bac\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/following/391580/391580.1_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2Ffollowing%2F391580%2F391580.1_.png&h=db293afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/following/391580/391580.2_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2Ffollowing%2F391580%2F391580.2_.png&h=e2a40638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/following/391580/391580.3_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2Ffollowing%2F391580%2F391580.3_.png&h=f5df127b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/following/391580/391580.4_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2